com.skratchdot.riff.wav
Interface SampleLoop

All Known Implementing Classes:
SampleLoopImpl
public interface SampleLoop

A representation of the model object 'Sample Loop'.

The following features are supported:

  • Cue Point ID
  • Type
  • Start
  • End
  • Fraction
  • Play Count

See Also:
WavPackage.getSampleLoop()
